{"tid":1391341,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[常識] 防毒面具密封測試","createTime":"2019-07-31T11:45:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T14:35:09.000Z","uid":201889,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8f8461118b5343567699e655dc5033659a84f92e","tid":1391341,"uid":201889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:45:57.000Z","msg":"每次戴防毒面具 (即使是 N95 紙口罩), 也 <span style=\"color: gold;\">一定</span> 要做 <span style=\"color: red;\">密封測試</span><br />\n<br />\n檢查目的是確定呼吸防護具是否有漏氣<br />\n若有任何漏氣的地方，則環境中有害空氣會不經處理而直接吸進人體，<br />\n因此在 <span style=\"color: gold;\">每次</span> 佩戴好防護具時，需進行防護具<span style=\"color: red;\">密封測試</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">密封測試</span> 分為兩部份 : <br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">1. 正壓檢查</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">2. 負壓檢查</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">正壓檢查</span></span><br />\n<br />\n佩戴者將出氣閥以手掌或其他適當方式封閉後，再緩慢吐氣<br />\n防毒面具應會輕微脹起<br />\n若面罩內的壓力能達到並維持脹起，空氣無向外洩露的現象，即表示面罩與臉頰密合良好<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://ehs.virginia.edu/ehs/ehs.chemicalsafety/chemicalsafety.images/respirator_positive_fit_test.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fehs.virginia.edu%2Fehs%2Fehs.chemicalsafety%2Fchemicalsafety.images%2Frespirator_positive_fit_test.jpg&h=dcd77f2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">負壓檢查</span></span><br />\n<br />\n佩戴者使用適當的方式阻斷進氣（如：濾罐的進氣口處），再緩慢吸氣，使得面罩輕微凹陷。<br />\n<br />\n若在十秒鐘內面體仍保持輕微凹陷，且無空氣內洩的跡象，即可判定該面罩通過檢查<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://ehs.virginia.edu/ehs/ehs.chemicalsafety/chemicalsafety.images/respirator_negative_fit_test.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fehs.virginia.edu%2Fehs%2Fehs.chemicalsafety%2Fchemicalsafety.images%2Frespirator_negative_fit_test.jpg&h=fc072e01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7aa01e35e5b8027735456ac7fbea4efd010aa3b6","tid":1391341,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:50:55.000Z","msg":"【攬炒】水炮車又有乜好怕喎！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1391293\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1391293</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"979c4f4097cf5785602c97b61acded3aa13c0407","tid":1391341,"uid":81996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:52:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e192406aadc8228900b07468740b160ebc906eb4","tid":1391341,"uid":649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:52:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4adacbd57f23fb2e58ce04e6b82b57d830041734","tid":1391341,"uid":25661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T11:55:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c9d1e389160f22086d02b27f213b59ed6422065","tid":1391341,"uid":205763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T12:20:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4884c7ceb27838ae5c975b4de2b62a6978f6ae26","tid":1391341,"uid":272353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:13:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e80dfc8d126c730d74ca76ecf3254d253a5432b8","tid":1391341,"uid":3194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:35:09.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"}]}